<TR><TD>This can be found in <a href="ftp://ftp.void.jump.org/pub/sinclair/magazines/YourSinclair/Issue71/Tape/">this issue of Pokerama</a>.
 <i>(Cover Tape in Your Sinclair issue 71)</i> 
